Title: The Fallen Woman
Plot: A woman is found wearing an angel costume dead.  Crews and Reese must figure out if it was suicide or murder.  They find out the victim might have been involved in a scam involving Russian brides.  The big problem they face is that they can't get to the ringleader.
GuestStars: James Moses Black, Michael David Cheng, Jillian Difusco, Shashawnee Hall, Natalina Maggio, Chris J. Nelson, Adam Pilver, Chris Symonds, Michael Symonds, Jai Thangkeaw, James Harvey Ward, Holly Weber, Jennifer Lee
